                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-38-18591128 t18591128-38-punishment-36"></join>Confined Twelve. Months.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">There was another indictment against the prisoner.</hi>
